OL,3,CVictims of Miami Showband massacre
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,FThe legacy of the Miami Showband is
OL,7,Fabout more than just music, it is
OL,8,Fbringing people together, a survivor
OL,9,Fof the loyalist ambush which targeted
OL,10,Fits members has said.
OL,12,FSinger Fran O'Toole, guitarist Tony
OL,13,FGeraghty and trumpeter Brian McCoy
OL,14,Fwere shot dead on a roadside close to
OL,15,FNewry on July 31 1975 after having
OL,16,Fbeen pulled over at a bogus security
OL,17,Fforces checkpoint.
