OL,3,CVictims of Miami Showband massacre
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,FTwo of the loyalist terrorists from
OL,7,Fthe Ulster Volunteer Force were also
OL,8,Fkilled in the incident, when a bomb
OL,9,Fthey placed on the bus exploded
OL,10,Fprematurely.
OL,12,FSurvivors Des Lee and Stephen Travers
OL,13,Fwere among those who gathered at the
OL,14,Froadside where the atrocity happened
OL,15,Fon Thursday to remember their
OL,16,Fbandmates.
OL,18,FIt was the first of a series of
OL,19,Fevents, including in Newry and Dublin,
OL,20,Fbeing held on Thursday to mark the
OL,21,F50th anniversary.
