OL,6,FMr Travers said 50 years of tears have
OL,7,Fdried up and they want to tell the
OL,8,Fwhole world of the legacy of the Miami
OL,9,FShowband.
OL,11,F"It's far more than a band at this
OL,12,Fstage because bands come and go, and
OL,13,Fmusic comes and goes, and styles
OL,14,Fchange, and if you were to ask anybody
OL,15,Funder 50 years of age to name all of
OL,16,Fthe members of the Rolling Stones, I'm
OL,17,Fsure they'd have a problem," he said.
