OL,6,F"These things come and go, but the
OL,7,Flegacy of the Miami Showband is one
OL,8,Fthat I am enormously proud of, and it
OL,9,Fis simply this: when people came to
OL,10,Fsee us, whether they were Catholic,
OL,11,FProtestant, Unionist, Nationalist,
OL,12,Fthey left sectarianism outside the
OL,13,Fdoor of the dance hall and they saw
OL,14,Feach other as human beings, and they
OL,15,Fdanced with each other, and sometimes
OL,16,Fthey even fell in love."
