OL,3,CVictims of Miami Showband massacre
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,F"I commend you all for your commitment
OL,7,Fto remembering your friends by
OL,8,Fcelebrating their lives and the joy of
OL,9,Fmusic they brought to so many in their
OL,10,Ftragically short lives, I truly hope
OL,11,Fthat while never forgetting the pain
OL,12,Fof the past we continue to move
OL,13,Fforward as a society towards a
OL,14,Fpeaceful, inclusive and better future
OL,15,Ffor all of our people," she said.
OL,17,FEarlier, Mr Lee said he remembers
OL,18,F"every single thing in the finest
OL,19,Fdetail" from the atrocity in 1975.
