OL,3,CVictims of Miami Showband massacre
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,F"It was the most horrendous scene I
OL,7,Fhave ever seen in my life, when I got
OL,8,Fup off the grass and I had to make a
OL,9,Frun up that embankment to get help.
OL,11,F"When I got onto the main road, it was
OL,12,Fthe worst sight anyone could ever
OL,13,Fimagine," he told the BBC Radio Ulster.
OL,15,F"They were my brothers, you know,
OL,16,Fthree of my brothers."
