OL,6,FWhile there has been criticism of a
OL,7,Floyalist band parade planned to take
OL,8,Fplace in Portadown on Saturday to
OL,9,Fremember one of the attackers, Mr Lee
OL,10,Fsaid he has "no problem with that
OL,11,Fwhatsoever".
OL,13,F"They are entitled to commemorate
OL,14,Ftheir dead as much as we are entitled
OL,15,Fto commemorate ours," he said.
OL,17,FHe was, however, critical of the UK
OL,18,FGovernment over its handling of the
OL,19,Fpast, saying he feels they are doing a
OL,20,F"dreadful job".
