OL,3,CVictims of Miami Showband massacre
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,F"They're trying to push all the
OL,7,Ffamilies under the carpet and hope
OL,8,Fthat it all goes away, and as long as
OL,9,FI'm alive, I will fight for Fran,
OL,10,FBrian and Tony," he said.
OL,12,FMr Lee said he expected the
OL,13,Fanniversary will be an "extremely
OL,14,Fdifficult day".
OL,16,F"My whole philosophy in life now is
OL,17,Fforgive and forget and move on," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
