OL,3,CVictims of Miami Showband massacre
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,F"I don't hold any grudge. What
OL,7,Fhappened to my friends was appalling
OL,8,Fbut I don't want to live for the rest
OL,9,Fof my life living in the past.
OL,11,F"But there's one thing we must never
OL,12,Fforget: Fran O'Toole, Brian McCoy and
OL,13,FTony Geraghty."
OL,15,FHe described their only weapons as
OL,16,Fhaving been instruments to entertain
OL,17,Faudiences "during that awful time" in
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland in the 1970s.
