OL,3,CVictims of Miami Showband massacre
OL,4,Cremembered 50 years on
OL,6,F"Fran had a microphone, Brian had a
OL,7,Ftrumpet, and Tony had a guitar. That
OL,8,Fwas the weapons that they had during
OL,9,Fthat awful time in Northern Ireland,
OL,10,Fbringing two hours of peace and joy
OL,11,Fand happiness and dance and love and
OL,12,Fkindness and everything that went with
OL,13,Fit," he said.
OL,15,F"That was our job to entertain those
OL,16,Fpeople for two hours, no matter what
OL,17,Freligion, no matter what creed.
